item.title: Workout Exporter Privacy Policy
item.description: Workout Exporter Privacy Policy The Workout Exporter privacy policy is extremely simple: We don't share your activity data with anyone at all except when you decide to do so yourself by sharing an activity on Facebook, dailymile, twitter, emails, sms etc. Non-identifiable usage analytics are tracked using TestFlight.
